06/04/2005
ANTALYA, Turkey -- NATO Assistant Secretary General for Political Affairs Guenther Altenburg praised the key role Turkey plays in the Pact, during a speech Tuesday (5 April) at the 15th International Security and Co-operation Conference. He added that the Alliance is seeking to expand co-operation with the countries of the Black Sea, the Middle East and North Africa. (Turks.US, AP - 05/04/05)
